{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2391 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2391 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[597,617],"content":"Compiler Error C2391","linkify":"Compiler Error C2391","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2391","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'identifier' : 'friend' cannot be used during type definition","pos":[618,679]},{"content":"The <ph id=\"ph1\">`friend`</ph> declaration includes a complete class declaration.","pos":[686,749],"source":"The `friend` declaration includes a complete class declaration."},{"content":"A <ph id=\"ph1\">`friend`</ph> declaration can specify a member function or an elaborated type specifier, but not a complete class declaration.","pos":[750,873],"source":" A `friend` declaration can specify a member function or an elaborated type specifier, but not a complete class declaration."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2326:","pos":[880,917]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2391 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2391\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2391\"\nms.assetid: 63a9c6b9-03cc-4517-885c-bdcd048643b3\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2391\n'identifier' : 'friend' cannot be used during type definition  \n  \n The `friend` declaration includes a complete class declaration. A `friend` declaration can specify a member function or an elaborated type specifier, but not a complete class declaration.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2326:  \n  \n```  \n// C2391.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \nclass D {   \n   void func( int );   \n};  \n  \nclass A {  \n   friend class B { int i; };   // C2391  \n  \n   // OK  \n   friend class C;  \n   friend void D::func(int);  \n};  \n```"}